mixin experience
  section.experience
    .experience__item
      .experience__container.experience__container--width
        .experience__content
          .experience__item-title Team over <span class="experience__title-span">17</span> <span class="experience__title-span">years</span> of experience
          p.experience__paragraph Developing the business projects of our Clients, GEM Expo exports its services to the most prestigious exhibition centers of the World and offers its Clients a comprehensive service around the World at the highest professional level
        picture.experience__img
          img(src="./assets/images/experience__img1.png" alt="experience__img1" srcset="./assets/images/experience__img1_X2.webp 2x")
    .experience__item.experience__item--margin
      .page-container.experience__container.experience__container--justify-end
        picture.experience__img.experience__img--position.experience__img--size
          img(src="./assets/images/exp__img2.png" alt="experience__img2")
        .experience__content.experience__content--black.experience__content--padding
          p.experience__paragraph.experience__paragraph--white.experience__paragraph--width We are ready to develop and increase the success of our Clients together in exhibition, advertising,expo and event projects, which are based on a strong team of professionals, ambitious goals, modern technologies, where our satisfied Clients are our main motivation.
          p.experience__paragraph.experience__paragraph--white.experience__paragraph--width We will be glad to become your strategic Partner for Expo and Event projects in Russia.